      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride that still has plenty of life left? This car is a solid, reliable performer that has been well-used and shows some character, but it's ready to get you where you need to go! It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a dependable vehicle at a great price.",
